      "text": "わわっ……！",
      "startTime": 20.9000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "なんですか、突然大きな声を出して\nあ……なるほど、そういうことですか……",
      "startTime": 26.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ゆ、床に大量の髪の毛が……\n結構バッサリいってしまったぞ……",
      "startTime": 35.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "……私のせいじゃないですから\n大体、こんな所で髪を切る方が悪いんです",
      "startTime": 41.2686036788,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "確かにそうですね……最近忙しくて髪を切りに行く\n時間がなくて……すみません",
      "startTime": 49.7407381907,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_07_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "いくら時間がなくても自分で髪を切るなんて\nアイドルのマネージャーとして恥ずかしくないんですか",
      "startTime": 56.6,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
